        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "2. To aggravate their spiritual whoredom, as being committed in the sight and presence of their Lord and Husband, whose eye is alone peculiarly upon them in all their ways, than it is upon other people. Or, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
