      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "3. By way of opposition unto men’s judgment. Idolatry ofttimes seems good, and reasonable, and religious in the eyes of men, but, saith he, it is evil in the eyes of the Lord, whose judgment is most considerable. ",
        "children": []
